OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779393955
OL,3,CReplacement gate for QEII Marina could
OL,4,Ccost #10.7 million
OL,6,FUp to #10.7 million could be spent on
OL,7,Fa new gate for Guernsey's Queen
OL,8,FElizabeth II Marina.
OL,10,FThe States' Trading Supervisory Board
OL,11,F(STSB) has put forward a funding
OL,12,Fproposal, with up to #5.35 million
OL,13,Ffrom the General Revenue Reserve and
OL,14,Fthe same again as a bank loan.
OL,16,FIt will need to be voted through by
OL,17,Fpoliticians and the STSB says time is
OL,18,Fof the essence to do something.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
