CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779393955
OL,3,CReplacement gate for QEII Marina could
OL,4,Ccost #10.7 million
OL,6,FThe marina is the island's largest,
OL,7,Fwith space for more than 700 boats,
OL,8,Fbut the gates are now 40 years old and
OL,9,Fin urgent need of repair.
OL,11,FWithout action, the Committee says
OL,12,F"their condition will continue to
OL,13,Fdeteriorate" with "a high likelihood
OL,14,Fthat they will fail beyond repair".
OL,16,FThey warn that this would make the
OL,17,Fmarina "unsuitable for a very large
OL,18,Fnumber of current berth holders" and
OL,19,Fbe a "significant, material risk to
OL,20,FGuernsey Ports' finances", as well as
OL,21,Freputationally damaging.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779393955
OL,3,CReplacement gate for QEII Marina could
OL,4,Ccost #10.7 million
OL,6,FFixing the current infrastructure is
OL,7,Flikely to be cheaper, but not last as
OL,8,Flong as a full replacement.
OL,10,FThe STSB says it does not have a
OL,11,Fpreferred option of what to do but
OL,12,Fwants funds approved for a new gate,
OL,13,Fin case that proves to be the best
OL,14,Fchoice once contractors tender their
OL,15,Fplans - with Policy and Resources
OL,16,Fnominated to be the final decision
OL,17,Fmakers once a business case is
OL,18,Fapproved.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/5
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
