OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,390,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F389A1779393955
OL,3,CReplacement gate for QEII Marina could
OL,4,Ccost #10.7 million
OL,6,FThe policy letter states that Guernsey
OL,7,FPorts would not be able to fund these
OL,8,Fimprovements alone, without
OL,9,Fsignificantly increasing user fees or
OL,10,Fimpacting other key priorities.
OL,12,FIf government funding is given the
OL,13,Fgreen light, it is hoped that
OL,14,Fconstruction could be finished by the
OL,15,Fend of next year.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/5
